    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Ok, I understand. I'm in favor of an `afterInit` to stay consistent with the vocabulary we are already using in the widgets.\n\nI'm not so sure about the `afterFirstRender`, some widgets might not render while other are rendered (because we can set the `hideIfNoResult`-like attributes to individual widgets).\n",
