  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We could just have a `afterRender` since we're likely to use event emitters and they support `once`. This could be : \n\n``` js\ninstantsearch().once('afterRender', fadeInUISomeStuff);\n```\n\n@pixelastic : it's an instant search wide event proposition, not one for widgets.\n",
