  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "`ready` is meaningless in our case. Its semantic comes from the DOM, which is irrelevant here. Maybe if we have something like afterResults or afterSearch? (for `afterRender`)\n\nThose are advanced feature anyway, and they will require some user willingness to learn the concepts of the library. Let's make it so we don't have the user learn too much by reusing the same concepts.\n",
